Money Stuff =0A One of the main problems in finance is the principal-agent =
problem, and one =0Aof the main forms that it takes is steak dinners. You a=
re sellin =0A=0A=0A <https://bloom.bg/4hjD5dS> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomber=
g.com/click=3Fs=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12821888&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615=
cf44233be620525&p=3D03062025>=0A=0A=0A=0AFirst Trust=0A=0AOne of the main p=
roblems in finance is the principal-agent problem, and one of =0Athe main f=
orms that it takes is steak dinners. You are selling a product, and =0Ayou =
want someone to buy it. The person making the buying decision is not =0Anec=
essarily the person paying for the product, or the person who will benefit =
