hat.=C2=A0</p> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway Graffeo and Abelson writ=
e:</p> <blockquote> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Internal emails reviewed b=
y Bloomberg Businessweek and an investigation by the Financial Industry Reg=
