style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[Other ETF issuers] began undercutting one anothe=
r=E2=80=99s fees, charging customers less and less, then almost nothing. Fi=
rst Trust excused itself from the race to the lowest fees, sticking with co=
mparatively high rates and winning business across the country anyhow, than=
ks in part to its sales force.</p> </blockquote> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0=
