iness of the recipient=E2=80=99s employer.=E2=80=9D They can=E2=80=99t offe=
r meals and entertainment that are frequent or lavish enough to =E2=80=9Cra=
ise any question of propriety=E2=80=9D=E2=80=94a definition firms must inte=
